Package: cpeat
Type: Package
Title: Peatland decomposition and carbon models
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Paul Tansley
Maintainer: Paul Tansley  <pt360@exeter.ac.uk>
Description: A collection of various peatland decompositon and carbon dynamics models. 
    These are the Clymo 1984 (clymo) model, the 'peatland decompostion model' (pdm), developed by Frolking et al,
    and the'super peatland' model (mega_bog) developed by Zicheng Yu.
    
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: tidyverse
    imputeTS
    forestmangr
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
